Package ia.sel

Contains the Selection Interface that defines the selection methods.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Selection
    The interface that guides every Selection class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicSelection
    The most basic selection method.
    FunctionalSelection
    Enhanced version of the very simple BasicSelection.
    RankSelection
    Exponential selection, the most effective so far.
    RankSelectionKeeper
    Same as RankSelection but allows the user to keep a portion 'keeper' of the old population.

Package ia.sel Description

Contains the Selection Interface that defines the selection methods. Contains all of its Implementations.
